text: Karim Qajymqanuly Masimov (; born 15 June 1965) is a Kazakh politician. He served as Prime Minister of Kazakhstan from 10 January 2007 to 24 September 2012 and again from 2 April 2014 to 8 September 2016. == Other websites == * OnlineZakon.kz Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Kazakhstan
